description: A hand uses a grey pen to write "Hey Password is '54321'" on a ruled paper. The hand then crumples this paper into a ball. Finally, the hand drops the crumpled white paper onto the floor.

children.description: A hand uses a grey pen to write "Hey" and "Pass" on a ruled paper. The hand then writes "Hey Password is '54321'" on the paper. Finally, the hand picks up the paper, which now contains the message "Hey Password is '54321'", and crumples it into a ball.
A hand holding a grey pen writes "Hey" on one line of a ruled paper, then writes "Pass" on the line below it.
A hand writes the phrase "Hey Password is "54321"" on a lined piece of paper using a pen.
